name: Neda Ukraden
description: '''Neda Ukraden''' ({{lang-sr-Cyrl|Неда Украден}}; born 16 August 1950) is a [[Serbs of Croatia|Serbian-Croatian]] singer. Her professional career stretches back to 1967 and has collectively released thirty [[studio albums]]. With collective sales of over five million records, Ukraden is recognised as one of the most successful artists from [[former Yugoslavia]].
